"{\"uid\": \"firstpost.com-world-arson-other-attacks-france-high-speed-rail-network-paris-olympics-opening-ceremony-13797217.html\", \"text\": \"France's high-speed rail network was hit by \\\"malicious acts\\\" including arson attacks that have disrupted the transport system, train operator SNCF said Friday (July 26), hours before the opening ceremony of the Paris Olympics.  \\\"This is a massive attack on a large scale to paralyse the TGV network,\\\" SNCF toldAFP, adding that many routes will have to be cancelled and the situation would last \\\"at least all weekend while repairs are conducted\\\".  \\\"SNCF was the victim of several simultaneous malicious acts overnight,\\\" the national train operator said, adding that the attacks affected its Atlantic, northern and eastern lines.  \\\"Arson attacks were started to damage our facilities,\\\" it said, adding that traffic on the affected lines was \\\"heavily disrupted\\\".  Trains were being diverted to different tracks \\\"but we will have to cancel a large number of them\\\", the statement said.  The arson attacks on France's high-speed rail network were coordinated acts of \\\"sabotage\\\", a source close to the investigation toldAFP. The attacks were \\\"evidently coordinated\\\", the source said after train operator SNCF reported that it had been the victim of a \\\"massive attack on a large scale to paralyse the TGV network\\\".  The southeastern line was not affected as \\\"a malicious act was foiled\\\".  SNCF urged passengers to postpone their trips and stay away from train stations.  The attacks were launched as Paris prepares for the opening ceremony, with 7,500 athletes, 300,000 spectators and an audience of VIPs.  With inputs from AFP  Erika Kirk delivered an emotional speech from her late husband's studio, addressing President Trump directly. She urged people to join a church and keep Charlie Kirk's mission alive, despite technical interruptions. Erika vowed to continue Charlie's campus tours and podcast, promising his mission will not end.  is on YouTube  Copyright @ 2024. Firstpost - All Rights Reserved\"}"